# Mock API mode

The app can run fully frontend-only via `VITE_USE_MOCK_API=true`.

- Real Laravel repositories live in `*ApiRepository.ts` (do not delete).
- Mock implementations live in `*MockRepository.ts` and read `/public/mocks/*.json`.
- Barrel files (`*Repository.ts`) switch between mock and API using `isMockApiEnabled()`.
- Auth / saved / owner mutations persist in `localStorage` while mocking.

To rewire Laravel later: set `VITE_USE_MOCK_API=false` and point `VITE_API_BASE_URL` at the backend.
